Description:
    Generates the daemon files to run the processing of updates by a daemon.

    This generator is based on git://github.com/dougal/daemon_generator.git

Example:
    ./script/generate daemonized_solr_daemon

    This will create:
        lib/daemons
        script/daemons
        lib/daemons/daemonized_solr_processor.rb
        lib/daemons/daemonized_solr_processor_ctl
        config/daemons.yml
